text: 155 (one hundred fifty-five) is a natural number. It comes after 154 and before 156. == In mathematics == *155 is a semiprime number. This means it is the product of two prime numbers. Its prime factorization is: 155=5Ã—31 *In Roman numerals, 155 is written as CLV. == Other facts == *155 is the police emergency telephone number in Turkey. *The year AD 155 was a year in the Julian calendar (used in ancient Rome).
